				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "These ADs occur in the epilogue. In one set, Wulbren is admiring the stonework in front of him, and contemplating the artistry of Moonrise Towers. In the other, it's his idle behaviour as he prepares to leave for Baldur's Gate - excited for his plans to all come together."
